es nor decreases the probability of coverage or outage when all the\ntiers have the same target-SINR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Mar 2011 00:51:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2011 21:48:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Mar 2012 04:09:57 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 23 Dec 2012 23:09:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-18"}
