th the hot\nshocked plasma and ii) the rapid adiabatic expansion of the ejecta. The spatial\ndistribution of the radiative recombination continuum predicted by the\nnumerical model is in good agreement with that observed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Mar 2011 15:21:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
